entries.femaleVariant: You return. How? How you manage dis?
Disappointed?
Exactly what I want to talk to Brigitte about.
Wanna talk to Brigitte.
Tried to set me up, you shit.
Wanna talk to Brigitte, your boss.
Do that to every merc you hire – try to set 'em up?
<mothertongue l="creo" m="Koulèv Sal!" b="" a=" You believe netfachis?! What he say?"/>
That the other guy?
<mothertongue l="creo" m="chèfine" b="You think I let you near my " a=" after NetPig hack you? <Rich color=\"MainColors.ActiveBlue\">Bouzan Sal!</>"/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="creo" m="chèfine" b="You think I let you near my " a=" after NetPig hack you? <Rich color=\"MainColors.ActiveBlue\">Salopri!</>"/>

entries.femaleVariant: That him? That the scopsucker you sent into the mechdragon's den first?
He gonna, ugh... pull through?
Best you worry about yourself, not him!
Disappointed? You needed me to do my little trick and then you needed me to die.
Exactly what I aim to talk about… with Brigitte.
That the other one?
That the other guy you sent to the GIM?
Didn't make it, looks like.
You talk wid me now.
What de fuck you do in de GIM?
You were to hack de agent, not cut deal wid him!
<mothertongue l="creo" m="anndan." b="No, you say what happen. You say or I open you, see wid my own eyes what worm crawl " a=""/>
<mothertongue l="creo" m="anndan" b="You say or I open you, see wid my own eyes what worm crawl " a="."/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Li tounen." t="She's back." b="" a=""/>
entries.maleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Li tounen." t="He's back." b="" a=""/>

entries.femaleVariant: <mothertongue l="creo" m="Ase." b="" a=" We must head under."/>
I hope you will not lead her to de crypt?
entries.maleVariant: I hope you will not lead him to de crypt?

entries.femaleVariant: <mothertongue l="creo" m="ranyon" b="She is " a=". Nothing special. You see de scans."/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="creo" m="ranyon" b="He is " a=". Nothing special. You see de scans."/>

entries.femaleVariant: [Punch] Give it your best shot.
Haven't turned coat, not on NetWatch's side, here.
I fucking dare you.
entries.maleVariant: I fuckin' dare you.

entries.femaleVariant: Listen, I didn't turn coat, didn't pick a side. We made a deal, is all.
Did what you wanted, 'cept 'stead of gettin' my circuits acid-fried, I'm still breathin'. That so damn wrong?
entries.maleVariant: Did what you wanted, except 'stead of gettin' my circuits acid-fried, I'm still breathin'. That so damn wrong?

entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Bouzen estipid." t="Stupid bitch." b="" a=""/>
entries.maleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Bata estipid." t="Stupid fucker." b="" a=""/>

entries.femaleVariant: He bend you over, poke you, an' you come back smiling.
Tsss…
What did you do to me in the GIM?
Shoulda cut a deal with NetWatch, maybe.
Exact. And now I will know what went wrong.
<mothertongue l="creo" m="kamyonèt avec kamera" b="You no do your trick. You did not check " a="."/>
Ten NetWatch scum dead, network and BBSes destroyed…. but you walk out alive.
You let loose in the GIM... with what, exactly? A virus? A… vectored electromag impulse?
entries.maleVariant: You let loose in the GIM? With... what, exactly? A-a virus? A vectored electromag impulse?

entries.femaleVariant: Plain to see you fucked up, somewhere…
I maybe shoulda cut a deal with NetWatch.
And you do better wid Netpigs? Dey make you champion, not treat you like rotten meat?
I would've... if somebody hadn't flatlined me. Sorry, but lost the heart to do anything after that.
Looks like you fucked up.
What's Brigitte make of it all?
<mothertongue l="creo" m="kamyonèt" b="You no do your job. De " a=" to check."/>
I would've... if somebody hadn't flatlined me. Sorry, but lost the heart to do anything after that.
<mothertongue l="creo" m="Di m kijan." b="Yet you live. " a=" Ten NetWatch scum dead, the grid, BBSes destroyed… but you walk, you breathe…"/>
Ten NetWatch scum dead, the grid, BBSes destroyed… but you walk, you breathe… How?
I will know what went wrong.
'Cause dealing with you's gotten me shit. A slug to the brain, fell foul of NetWatch, and now I got you on my ass about who knows what.
<mothertongue l="creo" m="Di m kijan." b="Yet you live. " a=" Ten NetWatch scum dead, the grid, BBSes destroyed… but you walk, you breathe…"/>
<mothertongue l="creo" m="\"Ki vale limyè\"" b="It is called " a=" – he who swallow de light."/>
Ten NetWatch agent swallow it. It destroy de grid, de BBSes. But not you. You vomit light back up.
Saw it before my own fuses popped – your guys shredding tags on the NetWatch agents in Mosley's grid.
Then, after you.
Looks like I got no choice.
No. Rather check out my other options first.
Don't think I'm that desperate yet.
You said no other could help you.
Maybe I got other options I don't know about yet.
OK, fine. I'll give you access.
How do I know you won't screw me again?
Then... after you.
Looks like I got no choice.
Follow me.
Did you change your mind?
Does this mean...?
<mothertongue l="creo" m="Ase." b="" a=" We must head under."/>
You are worried about agents? Then shoot her in de head.
entries.maleVariant: You worried about agents? Then shoot him in de head.

entries.femaleVariant: <mothertongue l="creo" m="ranyon" b="I know. I scanned her. Only a normal, filthy " a="."/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="creo" m="ranyon" b="I know. I scanned him. Only a normal, filthy " a="."/>

entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Ale. Mennen moun yo nan kavo a." t="Go. Take the others to the crypt." b="" a=""/>
I do not know what dey put in her, what corruption is in her system!
entries.maleVariant: I do not know what dey put in him, what corruption is in his system!

entries.femaleVariant: You don't know what was in there to begin with. How much it is worth.
You know about the biochip, don't you?
You know about the biochip, don't you?
If it is functional, we offer you good price for it.
Biochip's not for sale.
Biochip's busted. That's why I'm here.
Biochip's not for sale.
Biochip's busted. That's why I'm here.
Plus, do you no good to take it by force. It's in shitty shape already.
Haven't found a single soul capable of gettin' this thing outta me without scramblin' my brain.
You commissioned the heist, so I figured you must know somethin'. You've gotta.
How do you know all dis? How did you find us?
Remember Evelyn Parker?
Can you help me or not?
Evelyn Parker – name ring a bell?
Listen, can you help me or not?
Yes, of course. But not here. We will go to de crypt… where you must give us access to de chip.
Ah, de doll... de whore.
You found us because she led you to us. She has proved not completely useless after all.
Seriously? You gonna hold me here by force?
entries.maleVariant: Heh, seriously? You gonna hold me here by force?

entries.femaleVariant: Leave her.
entries.maleVariant: Leave him.

entries.femaleVariant: That why you're talkin' to me now? 'Cause you know I got the biochip?
Not 'cause I saved your frozen ass?
If I was any ordinary "ranyon," you'd have dealt with me already.
Placide saw in you common trash from de streets. This is why he chose you.
But you knew about de chip. And still put yourself in danger in de GIM.
Mhm. Just like you. Only I came out of there on my own.
entries.maleVariant: Hmph. Just like you. Only I came out of there on my own.

entries.femaleVariant: I saw them.
Shoulda thought about that before you tried to kill me.
Not gonna let you dig around in my head.
You wanna dig around in my head? I dunno, I'm startin' to have some trust issues with you guys.
entries.maleVariant: You wanna dig around in my head? Huh, I dunno, I'm startin' to have some trust issues with you guys.

entries.femaleVariant: You came to us in a bad time.
That s'posed to be an apology?
Shoulda thought about that before you tried to kill me.
Once we have de data we need, we will do our best to help you.
Seriously? Haven't I done enough for you already?
Seriously? Haven't done enough for you already?
There is no other way. To remove it, we must first examine it.
'Cause if you fuck up you're left empty-handed? That it?
I gave my word. We will help you.
How do I know you won't cheat me again?
Come with me.
If I was here, da chip would never be in danger.
I thought you dead.
What the hell happened?
That was your plan, right?
What the hell happened?
Well, that was your plan, wasn't it? I outlive your need for me, you get me outta the picture. Flatline.
Your people? Who?
Bullshit.
No. You are confused. Mosley mess wid your head.
Fuck Mosley. Got eyes, I can see. I'm right, aren't I?
We lose de link. Dat was not our plan.
Saw you zeroin' agent tags. Don't tell me you didn't know what was goin' on. Don't tell me I didn't see what I saw.
You walk into war zone. You got hit. It is dat simple.
I had to free my people. Dey are most important to me. We try to save you too, but... Mosley... he was stronger than we think.
I wanna talk with Brigitte.
Bullshit.
<mothertongue l="creo" m="Um byen?" b="" a=" Whatchu gonna do about it?"/>
Your people? Who?
Brigitte, and others. NetWatch hold her frozen in ICE.
So you see – dis whole rotten job was in your interest. It was de only way you could talk wid Brigitte.
Jesus... Mighta been good to know that before you threw me into the fucking fire.
Brigitte – wanna talk to her.
I did the GIM job. That was our deal. You and me – our biz is done.
entries.maleVariant: I did the job. That was our deal. You and me – our biz is done.

entries.femaleVariant: For now, you talk wid me.
Want to dig around in my head again?
Hope I get along better with you than with Placide.
Placide and I... We never quite saw eye to eye.
Don't like bein' kept in the dark. And I swear, if I hear any more moody fuckin' mumblin'... Which reminds me – just what the fuck is a "ranyon"?
entries.maleVariant: Don't like bein' kept in the dark. Ugh, and I swear, if I hear any more moody fuckin' mumblin'... Which reminds me – just what the fuck is a "ranyon"?

entries.femaleVariant: I will explain all, first we must verify if the biochip is in good condition. If yes, we will offer a fair price for it.
And put the chip at risk? Again?
I hope you return before your time runs out.
OK, fine. I'll give you access.
entries.maleVariant: Fine. I'll give you access.

entries.femaleVariant: <mothertongue l="creo" m="Finalman." b="" a=" Come with me."/>
You cannnot fault me for Placide's actions, his decisions while I was trapped in de Net.
I have been honest with you all along.
Tell me what is going on, or I break you open and see myself!
<mothertongue l="creo" m="anndan." b="You say what happen. You say or I open you, see wid my own eyes what worm crawls " a=""/>
You set me up!
[Punch] You set me up.
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Bouzen sal!" t="You dirty bitch!" b="" a=""/>
entries.maleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Bata sal!" t="You dirty bastard!" b="" a=""/>

entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Ase!" t="Enough!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Men, ou te wè --" t="But you saw--" b="" a=""/>
<mothertongue l="creo" m="ranyon" b="Yes. But I also saw her scans. She is no " a="."/>
entries.maleVariant: <mothertongue l="creo" m="ranyon" b="Yes. But I also saw his scans. He is no " a="."/>

entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Kite nou." t="Leave us." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Voye pèp nou an anba a." t="Move our people down below." b="" a=""/>
How much you know from my scans?
This is not over. NetWatch will return.
Think you more clever than NetPig?
I do not know what NetWatch plans, but they are not done.
We are not safe here.
You must be Brigitte.
Sending Placide away just for little ol' me?
You must be Brigitte. Hard woman to find.
You have something for me.
You know about the biochip, don't you?
Yes, and we must check its condition.
Sendin' Placide away just for little ol' me?
entries.maleVariant: Heh. Sending Placide away just for little ol' me?

entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Soti, kounye a. Fè tout moun soti." t="Out, now. Get everyone out." b="" a=""/>
I did not want him to harm you. That we cannot allow.
How much you know from my scans?
More than Placide, I am sure.
You recognized the biochip 'cause you've been looking for it.
entries.maleVariant: You recognized the biochip 'cause you were lookin' for it.

entries.femaleVariant: We must examine you. If you survived the GIM, it is at the chip's cost.
You must be Brigitte.
You must be Brigitte. Hard woman to find.
You have something for me.
That why you're talkin' to me? The biochip?
Well?
V!
If it is in good condition, we offer you a fair price. Perhaps more for the... emotional toll.
You will get apology when you say how much you want for the chip. If it is in good condition, of course.
Biochip's not for sale.
Biochip was already damaged.
Hh, biochip's not for sale.
entries.maleVariant: Heh, biochip's not for sale.

entries.femaleVariant: And you're not rippin' it outta me. Thing was in shit shape already before I strolled into the GIM.
Chip's already taken some damage. That's why I'm here to begin with.
Not that bad. Problem is, no one I've talked to can yank it out without risk of death.
Seein' as you commissioned the thing's theft, figured you might know a way to help.
How do you know all dis? How did you find us?
It does not function?
I'll give you access.
Access is all yours. Want this thing outta my head ASAP.
Oh?
Meant nothin' but problems ever since Konpeki…
I'll give you access.
<mothertongue l="creo" m="ranyon" b="You tell me, " a="!"/>
